@startuml
title Simple Booking Process Sequence

autonumber
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor Client
participant "Client App" as ClientApp
participant "Backend API" as API
participant "Cloudinary" as Cloudinary
participant "Provider App" as ProviderApp
actor Provider

Client -> ClientApp: Start reservation
Client -> ClientApp: Add description and before photos

loop Upload each before photo
  ClientApp -> Cloudinary: Upload photo
  Cloudinary --> ClientApp: Photo URL
end

Client -> ClientApp: See estimated price
Client -> ClientApp: Choose available date and time slot
Client -> ClientApp: Confirm reservation

ClientApp -> API: Create booking request\n(description, photos, price, time slot)
API -> ProviderApp: Notify provider\nnew booking request

Provider -> ProviderApp: Review request

alt Provider accepts offer
  ProviderApp -> API: Accept booking
  API -> API: Confirm booking\nand generate QR code
  API -> ClientApp: Notify client\nbooking confirmed
else Provider counters offer
  ProviderApp -> API: Send counter price
  API -> ClientApp: Notify client\ncounter offer
  Client -> ClientApp: Accept counter offer
  ClientApp -> API: Accept new price
  API -> API: Confirm booking\nand generate QR code
  API -> ProviderApp: Notify provider\nbooking confirmed
  API -> ClientApp: Notify client\nbooking confirmed
end

Client -> ClientApp: Open QR code\nat reserved time
ClientApp -> Client: Show QR code

Provider -> ProviderApp: Scan client QR code
ProviderApp -> API: Validate QR code
API -> API: Update booking to IN_PROGRESS
API -> ClientApp: Notify client\nservice started

Provider -> ProviderApp: Finish the job
Provider -> ProviderApp: Take after photos

loop Upload each after photo
  ProviderApp -> Cloudinary: Upload photo
  Cloudinary --> ProviderApp: Photo URL
end

ProviderApp -> API: Complete booking\nwith after photo URLs
API -> API: Update booking to COMPLETED
API -> ClientApp: Notify client\nservice completed

Client -> ClientApp: Leave review
ClientApp -> API: Submit rating and comment

alt Rating is high enough
  API -> ProviderApp: Notify provider\nreview received and +0.5 token reward
else Normal review
  API -> ProviderApp: Notify provider\nreview received
end

@enduml
